ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: SuiScan is a powerful app designed to help users discover and track new transactions on the Sui blockchain in real-time. It provides an intuitive interface for monitoring, analyzing, and exploring the latest Sui network activity.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: SuiScan connects directly to the Sui blockchain, continuously fetching and processing new transaction data. It uses advanced filtering and sorting algorithms to present users with the most relevant and recent transactions, making it easy to stay up-to-date with network activity.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: SuiScan offers a range of features including real-time transaction monitoring, customizable alerts, detailed transaction analysis, address tracking, and comprehensive search capabilities. Users can also view transaction history, track specific tokens, and export data for further analysis.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is SuiScan suitable for both beginners and advanced users?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Absolutely! SuiScan is designed with a user-friendly interface that caters to beginners, while also offering advanced features and data analysis tools for experienced users and developers. Whether you're new to Sui or a blockchain expert, SuiScan has something to offer.
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Got questions about our Sui transaction finder? We've got answers.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What is the Sui Transaction Finder?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: The Sui Transaction Finder is a powerful tool designed to help you discover and track new transactions on the Sui blockchain in real-time. It provides a user-friendly interface to search, filter, and analyze Sui transactions efficiently.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How do I use the Sui Transaction Finder?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Simply enter your search criteria, such as a wallet address, transaction type, or time range. Our app will instantly display matching transactions, allowing you to explore details and gain insights into Sui blockchain activity.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Is the Sui Transaction Finder free to use?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: We offer a free tier with basic features for all users. For advanced functionality and higher usage limits, we have premium plans available. Check our pricing page for more details.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How up-to-date is the transaction data?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Our app syncs with the Sui blockchain in near real-time, typically with a delay of just a few seconds. This ensures you have access to the most current transaction data available.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Can I receive alerts for specific transaction types?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Yes! Our app allows you to set up custom alerts for specific transaction types, addresses, or value thresholds. You can receive notifications via email, SMS, or push notifications to stay informed about important Sui blockchain activities.
